(229, 'yit-notifier-cache_nielsen', '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<notifier>\n    <latest>1.3.5</latest>\n    <update>10-14-2016</update>\n\n    <!--<dashboard ></dashboard>-->\n\n    <changelog>\n<![CDATA[\n<h4>Version 1.3.5 - Released on Oct 14, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Fixed: prevent fatal error with W3 Total Cache plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.4 - Released on Oct 12, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: WordPress 4.6.1 support</li>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.6.4 support</li>\n	<li>Updated: Visual Composer to 4.12.1 version</li>\n	<li>Updated: Essential Grid to 2.1.0.2 version</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Account & Refunds slogan compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.2 - Released on Jun 13, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.6 support</li>\n	<li>Updated: Visual Composer to 4.12 version</li>\n	<li>Updated: Slider Revolution to 5.2.5.3 version</li>\n	<li>Fixed: \"Product categpries slider\" doesn\' t show</li>\n	<li>Fixed: \"Items\" word not trabnslated on mini cart</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Parallax slider layout broken before page is completely loaded</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.1 - Released on May 05, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Updated: Slider Revolution to 5.2.5.1 version</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Theme loads slowly on back-end because of niubbys.altervista.org</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Wrong label on mini cart</li>\n	<li>Fixed: prevent notice on login page</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Wrong column number in product taxonomies page</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.0 - Released on Apr 22, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Custom logo support for WP 4.5</li>\n	<li>Updated: Visual Composer tp 4.11.2.1 version</li>\n	<li>Updated: Slider Revolution 5.2.5</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.12 - Released on Apr 14, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: WordPress 4.5 support</li>\n	<li>Updated: Visual Composer 4.11.2  (this update fix an issue with WPML)</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Ajax search not showed price and image on result box</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.11 - Released on Apr 06, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to YITH WooCommerce Advanced Product Options</li>\n	<li>Updated: Slider Revolution 5.2.4</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Translation issue with colors and label variations</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Notice for widgets with Php7</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Ajax search not showed price and image of the products</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.10 - Released on Mar 22, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.5.5 support</li>\n	<li>Updated: Slider Revolution 5.2.3.5</li>\n	<li>Updated: Visual Composer 4.11.1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.9 - Released on Mar 04, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added:WooCommerce 2.5.3 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.10</li>\n	<li>Added: Email option to share shortcode</li>\n	<li>Fixed: custom.css 404 error with child theme</li>\n	<li>Fixed: YITH WooCommerce Colors and label variation issue with custom attribute</li>\n	<li>Fixed: YITH WooCommere Add to Cart Popup compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.8 - Released on Feb 08, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Option \"Send Email to product vendor\" for YITH WooCommerce Multi Vendor</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Double icons on product loop</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Prevent wishlist notice on product loop</li>\n	<li>Fixed: YITH WooCommerce Ajax search autocomplete issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.7 - Released on Feb 02, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.5.2 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.9.2 support</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Shop by category menu on mobile issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.6 - Released on Jan 11, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.5 support(tested with 2.5.0 RC-1 version)</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.9.1 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Revolution Slider 5.1.6 support</li>\n	<li>Added: \"Linkedin\" on team member social\' s list</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Double title on WooCommerce Category loop</li>\n	<li>Fixed: YITH WooCommerce Compare compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.5 - Released on Dec 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: WordPress 4.4 support</li>\n    <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.4.12 support</li>\n    <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.5 support(tested with 2.5.0 beta 2 version)</li>\n    <li>Added: Visual Composer 4.9 support</li>\n    <li>Added: Revolution Slider 5.1.4 support</li>\n    <li>Fixed: YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote compatibility ( now the button have two different style )</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.4 - Released on Nov 03, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Visual Composer 4.8.0.1 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Revolution Slider 5.1 support</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH Essential Kit for WooCommerce #1 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Option \'Show categories description\' on theme option to show the category description</li>\n	<li>Added: Title tag support</li>\n	<li>Fixed: YITH WooCommerce Product Countdown widget issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.3 - Released on Oct 06, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Visual Composer 4.7.4 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Revolution Slider 5.0.9 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Essential Grid 2.0.9.1 support</li>\n	<li>Added: wc_extra_sorting_options compatiblity</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Favicon</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.2 - Released on Sep 04, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Visual Composer 4.7</li>\n    <li>Added: Revolution Slider 5.0.6</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Option \'Show products title\' in shop page</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Products variable add to cart template</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Update fragments in quick view after add to cart action</li>\n    <li>Fixed: \'Redirect to cart\' options in quick view after add to cart action</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Parse error when activating contact-form module</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Fatal error when try to activate plugins framework like yit-contact-form, yit-newsletter etc..</li>\n    <li>Fixed: WP Customizer doesn\'t display shortcodes</li>\n    <li>Updated: New enqueue style system for child theme ( ref. https://codex.wordpress.org/Child_Themes )</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 - Released on Aug 17, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.4.4 compatibility</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.6.2</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Wpml custom tab compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.0 - Released on Aug 11, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: Wordpress 4.3.x ready ( tested with 4.3 RC-2 version)</li>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.4.1 compatibility</li>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.13 compatibility</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.6.2</li>\n	<li>Added: option to Teaser shortcode to make it entirely clickable</li>\n	<li>Added: YIT PLUGINS(like portfolio, slider, testimonial etc.) as Modules</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Wpml Compatibility</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Shop by category on mobile devices</li>\n	<li>Fixed: WooCommerce Composite Products compatibility</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Vertical menu issue</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Infinite Scrolling issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.1 - Released on Jun 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.11 compatibility</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.5.3</li>\n	<li>Updated: prettyPhoto to 3.1.6 - latest stable and secure version</li>\n	<li>Fixed: custom style issue on multisite installation</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 - Released on Jun 11, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.10 compatibility</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH Infinite Scrolling</li>\n	<li>Fixed: plugins activations advice issue for premium plugins</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.9 - Released on May 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.9 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.5.2</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Social Login</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Multi Vendor</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH Live Chat</li>\n	<li>Added: FontAwesome icons dropdwon for \"Contact Info\" shortcode</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Wpml endpoint issue</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Shop Breadcrumb issue</li>\n	<li>Fixed: prettyPhoto layout with visual composer shortcode</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.8 - Released on May 11, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.5.1</li>\n	<li>Added: Essential Grid 2.0.9</li>\n	<li>Added: Revolution Slider 4.6.93</li>\n	<li>Added: Support to YITH WooCommerce Multi Vendor</li>\n	<li>Added: Support to YITH WooCommerce Wishlist v. 2.0.7</li>\n	<li>Added: Support to YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews v. 1.1.1</li>\n	<li>Fixed: \'woocommerce_stock_html\' filter arg issue</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Product Categories Slider shortcode issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.7 - Released on Apr 20, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: Wordpress 4.2 support</li>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.8 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.4.4</li>\n	<li>Added: Revolution Slider 4.6.9</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote, note* compatibility from 1.0.2 version</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Catalogue Mode</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Pdf Invoice</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Cart Message</li>\n	<li>Adedd: YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews</li>\n	<li>Adedd: YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Stripe</li>\n	<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Authorize.net</li>\n	<li>Added: Option \'Make the minicart scrollable\'</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Wp Security Issue</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Woocommerce Sale Flash Pro compatibility</li>\n	<li>Fixed: \"Product Categories\" and \"Categories Slider\" shortcodes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.6 - Released on Mar 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.7 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Essential Grid 2.0.8</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.4.3</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Logout url</li>\n	<li>Fixed: \"Woocommerce product addons\" compatibility issue</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Prelaunch Newsletter  issue with mailchimp configuration</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.5 - Released on Feb 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: Woocommerce 2.3.4 support</li>\n    <li>Added: \"Bbm\" and Whatsup fields to \"Contact Info\" widget</li>\n    <li>Fixed: redirect url after customer logout</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: Wordpress 4.1 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Woocommerce 2.2.10 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Revolution Slider 4.6.5  support</li>\n	<li>Added: Multiple choice categories for \"Products Tabs\" and \"Products Slider\" shortcodes</li>\n	<li>Added: Linkedin to \"share\" shortcode</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Single product show tab \"product inquiry\" by default</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Widget dropdown option doesn\'t work with all widgets</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.4.1</li>\n	<li>Added: Essential Grid 2.0.4</li>\n	<li>Added: Option to Theme Option \"Show reviews tab opened\" allow user to open or not the reviews tab by default</li>\n	<li>Added: Attribute \"Filter Type\" to \"show_products\" shortcode allow user to filter by given id products list</li>\n	<li>Added: Filter to email share button subject</li>\n	<li>Updated: Framework plugin core</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Text domain in woocommerce template</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Layout product View All selector</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Show/hide Review from theme option</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Submenu in Category menu need double click to go and doesn\' t open properly in non home page</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Zoom Magnifier issue on mobile in single product page</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: Essential Grid 2.0.1</li>\n	<li>Updated: Framework plugin core</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Open Graph title</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Sticky Header logo and cart position</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Error yit_get_shop_categories (in customize)</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Error on Woocommerce login class without WC plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>Added: Essential Grid 2.0</li>\n	<li>Added: Revolution Slider 4.6.5</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.3.5</li>\n	<li>Updated: Framework plugin core</li>\n	<li>Updated: Lookbook extra images from Media Gallery</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Google map in product tab description</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Quick view in Safari</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n]]>\n    </changelog>\n</notifier>', 'yes'),
